snippet.title: Zone of the Enders: The 2nd Runner M∀RS - Debut Trailer (Short version)
snippet.description:
JEHUTY lives. And there, ANUBIS thrives.

 Zone of the Enders: The 2nd Runner returns with 4k resolution and VR support on PlayStation 4, PlayStation VR, and Steam.

 Official website: https://www.konami.com/games/zoe_mars/en/
